snippet.title: B99 - Official PS VR2 Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: B99 is coming to PS VR2 in summer 2023. Dive into the neon world of B99 and check out gameplay in this latest action-packed trailer, as well as the features available on PS VR2, including enhanced graphics, new game modes, new weapons, new enemies, new abilities, and new perspective.
